    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186370/extras/611709dce66acaf5415a368327765050.poster.avif?t=1761236334\" width=486 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186370/extras/611709dce66acaf5415a368327765050.webm?t=1761236334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186370/extras/611709dce66acaf5415a368327765050.mp4?t=1761236334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to dig deep into a world full of valuable resources and ancient treasures! In this thrilling mining adventure, you'll collect resources, craft new tools, and improve them as you explore diverse biomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your resources and buildings, plan your progression and optimise your production. The game offers many ways to progress and accommodates different styles of play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the game, you will be able to unlock new features, quests and achievements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new lands and define the map of the world. Each land comes with its unique challenges and opportunities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
